5
00:00:13,710 --> 00:00:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, any new developments with <i>him</i>?</font>

6
00:00:16,820 --> 00:00:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, uh, I don't know 
if I'd go that far, but...</font>

7
00:00:21,170 --> 00:00:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like we're a lot closer 
than we were before the summer.</font>

8
00:00:24,590 --> 00:00:27,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sure sounds like
a development to me.</font>

9
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I guess you're right.</font>

10
00:00:31,370 --> 00:00:35,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y'know, Kyoko-san, there's actually
