when he set his super record.</i></font>

86
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Can he match it?</i></font>

87
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}This genius sprinter will have 
to reach new heights to do so!</i></font>

88
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:56,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}His speed is starting to ratchet up 
as he negotiates the toll roads of Sector 1.</i></font>

89
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those aero changes 
are making a difference.</font>

90
00:04:58,980 --> 00:05:01,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Despite the speed, 
the chassis is looking real steady.</font>

91
00:05:02,610 --> 00:05:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is gonna be damn fast.</font>

92
00:05:04,790 --> 00:05:08,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unless he screws up at some point, 
this is gonna be one amazing lap time.</font>

93
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And we already have an attention flag!</i></font>

94
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The high-speed S-curve by Benten Rock 
is coming up, preceded by the Hydro Trap.</i></font>

95
00:05:18,810 --> 00:05:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The waterfall at the side of the course
becomes a river as it crosses the road.</i></font>

96
00:05:23,890 --> 00:05:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The force of the water 
when you hit it is pretty intense.</font>

97
00:05:27,290 --> 00:05:31,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you haven't built up your neck 
muscles, you can injure it easily.</font>

98
00:05:35,220 --> 00:05:39,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't feel the grip, which means 
I'm skating on top of the water.</i></font>

99
00:05:39,610 --> 00:05:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm hydroplaning.</i></font>

100
00:05:42,410 --> 00:05:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}He's through!</i></font>

101
00:05:44,070 --> 00:05:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Testing the limits of his now-wet tires,
 he blitzes past Benten Rock!</i></font>

102
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't have to worry too much here.
Kanata's a cut above in wet conditions.</font>

103
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He sure proved that 
when it rained at Ashinoko.</font>

104
00:05:58,670 --> 00:06:01,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 86 is maintaining a good pace.</i></font>

105
00:06:01,220 --> 00:06:04,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It goes without saying that 
he's quicker than last year's lap record.</i></font>

106
00:06:05,380 --> 00:06:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Plus, he's within a tenth 
of the 4 car's super record.</i></font>

107
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's no exaggeration to say 
he's going at nearly the same pace.</i></font>

108
00:06:14,010 --> 00:06:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The back half of Sector 1 has some of 
the highest average speeds for the course.</font>

109
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:23,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And someone on Kanata's level will exit
 that corner doing 150 kmph, easy.</font>

110
00:06:24,340 --> 00:06:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before the next corner, the 86's turbo
 oughta get it close to 200 kmph.</font>

111
00:06:28,790 --> 00:06:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The roads may not be bolt straight, 
but you keep picking up speed.</font>

112
00:06:31,990 --> 00:06:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People talk about the high 
average speed of Double Lane,</font>

113
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it doesn't have 
a proper straight on it.</font>

114
00:06:38,420 --> 00:06:39,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what makes it tricky.</font>

115
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can feel the impact being gently absorbed
 whenever I hit a bump.</i></font>

116
00:06:46,170 --> 00:06:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The car tightens up in response
 to downward force.</i></font>

117
00:06:51,150 --> 00:06:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>These reaction speeds are sublime, too.</i></font>

118
00:06:53,300 --> 00:06:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Incredible work, Mister Okuyama.</i></font>

119
00:06:56,050 --> 00:07:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the less the car's posture shifts,
the better I can use the tires.</i></font>

120
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:04,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This will be an incredible weapon 
in a street racing sport like MFG.</i></font>

121
00:07:04,470 --> 00:07:08,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 86 car sings its way 
through this high-speed section.</i></font>

122
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the gap to the 4 car's record
 is still only marginal.</i></font>

123
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:12,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The attention flag is still there.</i></font>

124
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:15,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Soon, Sector 1 
by the seaside will end,</i></font>

125
00:07:15,850 --> 00:07:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}and we'll be into 
the mountains of Sector 2.</i></font>

126
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:21,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And this blistering dead heat continues!</i></font>

127
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mountain section is the scary part.</font>

128
00:07:25,340 --> 00:07:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The average speed stays high, 
but the road conditions get worse and worse.</font>

129
00:07:29,860 --> 00:07:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unlike the toll roads, these are roads
 people work and live on.</font>

130
00:07:34,550 --> 00:07:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you take a corner doing 
over 150 kmph and hit a pothole,</font>

131
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your control goes right
 out the window.</font>

132
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I doubt even guys like Kanata and Sawatari
 can redline it around here.</font>

133
00:07:51,150 --> 00:07:55,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Are Sawatari Koki and Katagiri Kanata 
driving in another dimension?</i></font>

134
00:07:55,970 --> 00:08:00,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Their battle for supremacy continues, 
leaving all others in their dust.</i></font>

135
00:08:01,300 --> 00:08:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 86 is now a hundredth 
quicker than the record!</i></font>

136
00:08:05,010 --> 00:08:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And awaiting Katagiri Kanata 
on his astonishing run...</i></font>

137
00:08:09,620 --> 00:08:12,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There were earthquakes 
following the volcanic eruption,</font>

138
00:08:12,980 --> 00:08:16,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Road 135 was submerged 
by a sudden swell of groundwater,</font>

139
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">producing a waterfall that's one of 
two natural hazards on Double Lane.</font>

140
00:08:23,010 --> 00:08:25,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, there's the Hydro Trap
 down by the sea,</font>

141
00:08:25,770 --> 00:08:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and up here in the mountains...</font>

142
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:33,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Looming large after this high-speed left,</i></font>

143
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:37,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}it's Double Lane's famed Jumping Spot.</i></font>

144
00:08:52,730 --> 00:08:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dude got some serious air.</font>

145
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:57,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think he was right on 
the edge of the landing area.</font>

146
00:08:58,350 --> 00:09:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is part of what makes
 Kanata so amazing.</i></font>

147
00:09:01,990 --> 00:09:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's his first time landing Double Lane's jump,
 but he knew just what to do.</i></font>

148
00:09:07,350 --> 00:09:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's hard for people who haven't done it before
 to imagine how scary it is.</i></font>

149
00:09:11,810 --> 00:09:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At the top of the jump, 
you're even higher than the fence,</i></font>

150
00:09:15,860 --> 00:09:20,470
