322
00:17:42,420 --> 00:17:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...she made it very clear 
that she's racing in MFG</font>

323
00:17:46,170 --> 00:17:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to chase after her former lover,
 Kanata Rivington.</font>

324
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say what?!</font>

325
00:17:52,130 --> 00:17:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that <i>true</i>, Kanata? Damn, dude!
 You and the chick with the huge melons?</font>

326
00:17:58,230 --> 00:17:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's not.</font>

327
00:17:59,890 --> 00:18:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's completely untrue, in fact. 
A total fabrication, in other words.</font>

328
00:18:03,770 --> 00:18:08,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Given the personal nature of the info,
 I was inclined not to share it,</i></font>

329
00:18:09,070 --> 00:18:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}but she was quite keen 
to let it be known far and wide,</i></font>

330
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}so I've done as she asked.</i></font>

331
00:18:15,190 --> 00:18:17,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes no sense to me, Ogata-san.</font>

332
00:18:17,490 --> 00:18:20,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's a matter of privacy, 
shouldn't that apply to me, too?</font>

333
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:22,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet I have to put up with this nonsense.</font>

334
00:18:23,430 --> 00:18:27,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, in Japan, people tend to treat
 old news a bit faster and looser.</font>

335
00:18:27,950 --> 00:18:31,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, when a beautiful woman's involved, 
most people just get jealous.</font>

336
00:18:31,950 --> 00:18:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not really sure I want to be envied 
for something like this.</font>

337
00:18:37,090 --> 00:18:41,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Three. Two. One. Go!</i></font>

338
00:18:42,180 --> 00:18:43,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And she's off!</i></font>

339
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}She's sure to be the talk of the race.</i></font>

340
00:18:45,670 --> 00:18:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Katagiri Kanata's ex...</i></font>

341
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}...breaks into the high-speed battle
 that marks the end of summer!</i></font>

342
00:18:50,850 --> 00:18:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kanata said it wasn't true.</i></font>

343
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I trust him.</i></font>

344
00:18:56,900 --> 00:19:02,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But even though it's not true, announcing it
 to the whole world like that...</i></font>

345
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have no way of correcting the record.</i></font>

346
00:19:05,420 --> 00:19:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Repeat a lie long enough
and it becomes the truth.</i></font>

347
00:19:08,810 --> 00:19:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What are you trying to pull, Emma?</i></font>

348
00:19:11,290 --> 00:19:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Isn't it obvious what I'm doing? 
I'm trying to get attention.</i></font>

349
00:19:15,390 --> 00:19:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Being at the center of attention 
comes with being a racing driver.</i></font>

350
00:19:19,450 --> 00:19:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I'll capitalize on 
the value of your name.</i></font>

351
00:19:22,690 --> 00:19:25,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's your punishment 
for ignoring my affections.</i></font>

352
00:19:25,900 --> 00:19:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Time you learned your lesson, darling.</i></font>

353
00:19:28,790 --> 00:19:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Aston Martin, maker of 
iconic luxury sports cars.</i></font>

354
00:19:33,310 --> 00:19:38,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}She looks steady and on track 
to outpace last year's lap record.</i></font>

355
00:19:38,840 --> 00:19:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}She's in third at the checkpoint!</i></font>

356
00:19:40,470 --> 00:19:42,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's running <i>third</i>?</font>

357
00:19:42,520 --> 00:19:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That doesn't surprise me one bit.</font>

358
00:19:44,670 --> 00:19:46,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knowing her skills, 
it's the natural outcome.</font>

359
00:19:47,810 --> 00:19:51,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I remember how often you used 
to defy Fujiwara-sensei, Emma.</i></font>

360
00:19:52,280 --> 00:19:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But you followed his methodology 
even closer than I did.</i></font>

361
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:02,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The way you meticulously shift the car's
 weight. It's expertly done and fast.</i></font>

362
00:20:02,530 --> 00:20:04,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You've really improved.</i></font>

363
00:20:06,010 --> 00:20:10,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}To the shock of all, both car and driver
 are proving to be first-rate.</i></font>

364
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:14,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}She's carving her way through 
the Godly Fifteen's top drivers!</i></font>

365
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:18,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The skills of the RDRS alumni 
are making them outright menaces.</i></font>

366
00:20:18,850 --> 00:20:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For real? She was a driver?</font>

367
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the 624 enters Sector 2 
with the attention flag still up.</i></font>

368
00:20:27,780 --> 00:20:30,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A provisional third is still on the cards.</i></font>

369
00:20:32,290 --> 00:20:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One has to wonder what kind of meaning 
the number "624" has for her...</font>

370
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And when I asked, 
her answer was quite simple.</i></font>

371
00:20:39,130 --> 00:20:43,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's apparently her angel number.</i></font>

372
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:44,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's an "angel number"?</font>

373
00:20:45,250 --> 00:20:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a series of numbers 
that's supposed to be personally lucky.</font>

374
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you encounter a unique number
 in your daily life,</font>

375
00:20:53,470 --> 00:20:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's supposed to bring you good luck.</font>

376
00:20:56,420 --> 00:20:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The name comes from angels 
being the ones to tell you what it is.</font>

377
00:21:03,290 --> 00:21:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's over the Jumping Spot, 
and into Sector 3!</i></font>

378
00:21:07,190 --> 00:21:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The elegant coupe in 
British racing green screams along.</i></font>

379
00:21:11,970 --> 00:21:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}There's a wildness in 
those pretty blue eyes.</i></font>

380
00:21:14,410 --> 00:21:16,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emma Greene is roaring!</i></font>

381
00:21:17,250 --> 00:21:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kanata Rivington. 
This isn't where you belong.</i></font>

382
00:21:22,470 --> 00:21:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I'm going to teach you how cheap 
and insignificant your beloved MFG is.</i></font>

383
00:21:29,690 --> 00:21:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Open your eyes, Kanata. You should 
be aiming and climbing so much higher.</i></font>

384
00:21:36,150 --> 00:21:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I'm the only one who can 
share it all with you by your side.</i></font>

385
00:21:41,350 --> 00:21:44,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will not let you cheat on me
 with some Japanese girl.</i></font>

386
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:47,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i><font face="Times New Roman">Come back, my darling.</font></i></font>

387
